    public class Api : Pulumi.CustomResource

namespace Pulumi.Aws.AppMesh
{
    public class Mesh : Pulumi.CustomResource
    {
        public Mesh(string name, Pulumi.Aws.AppMesh.MeshArgs? args = null, Pulumi.CustomResourceOptions? options = null) { }
        [Pulumi.Output("arn")]
        public Pulumi.Output<string> Arn { get; }
        [Pulumi.Output("createdDate")]
        public Pulumi.Output<string> CreatedDate { get; }
        [Pulumi.Output("lastUpdatedDate")]
        public Pulumi.Output<string> LastUpdatedDate { get; }
        [Pulumi.Output("name")]
        public Pulumi.Output<string> Name { get; }
        [Pulumi.Output("spec")]
        public Pulumi.Output<Pulumi.Aws.AppMesh.Outputs.MeshSpec?> Spec { get; }
        [Pulumi.Output("tags")]
        public Pulumi.Output<System.Collections.Immutable.ImmutableDictionary<string, object>?> Tags { get; }
        public static Pulumi.Aws.AppMesh.Mesh Get(string name, Pulumi.Input<string> id, Pulumi.Aws.AppMesh.MeshState? state = null, Pulumi.CustomResourceOptions? options = null) { }

namespace Pulumi.Aws.ApplicationLoadBalancing.Inputs
{
    public sealed class ListenerDefaultActionArgs : Pulumi.ResourceArgs
    {
        public ListenerDefaultActionArgs() { }

        public readonly System.Collections.Immutable.ImmutableArray<string> Subnets;

    }

namespace Pulumi.Aws.Cognito.Outputs
{
    [Pulumi.OutputType]
    public sealed class IdentityPoolCognitoIdentityProvider
    {
        public readonly string? ClientId;
        public readonly string? ProviderName;
        public readonly bool? ServerSideTokenCheck;
    }
    [Pulumi.OutputType]
    public sealed class IdentityPoolRoleAttachmentRoleMapping
    {
        public readonly string? AmbiguousRoleResolution;
        public readonly string IdentityProvider;
        public readonly System.Collections.Immutable.ImmutableArray<Pulumi.Aws.Cognito.Outputs.IdentityPoolRoleAttachmentRoleMappingMappingRule> MappingRules;
        public readonly string Type;
    }
    [Pulumi.OutputType]
    public sealed class IdentityPoolRoleAttachmentRoleMappingMappingRule
    {
        public readonly string Claim;
        public readonly string MatchType;
        public readonly string RoleArn;
        public readonly string Value;
    }
    [Pulumi.OutputType]

        public Pulumi.Output<System.Collections.Immutable.ImmutableArray<Pulumi.Aws.Ecs.Outputs.TaskDefinitionVolume>> Volumes { get; }

namespace Pulumi.Aws.Efs

    public class FileSystem : Pulumi.CustomResource
    {
        public FileSystem(string name, Pulumi.Aws.Efs.FileSystemArgs? args = null, Pulumi.CustomResourceOptions? options = null) { }
        [Pulumi.Output("arn")]
        public Pulumi.Output<string> Arn { get; }
        [Pulumi.Output("creationToken")]
        public Pulumi.Output<string> CreationToken { get; }
        [Pulumi.Output("dnsName")]
        public Pulumi.Output<string> DnsName { get; }
        [Pulumi.Output("encrypted")]
        public Pulumi.Output<bool> Encrypted { get; }
        [Pulumi.Output("kmsKeyId")]
        public Pulumi.Output<string> KmsKeyId { get; }
        [Pulumi.Output("lifecyclePolicy")]
        public Pulumi.Output<Pulumi.Aws.Efs.Outputs.FileSystemLifecyclePolicy?> LifecyclePolicy { get; }
        [Pulumi.Output("performanceMode")]
        public Pulumi.Output<string> PerformanceMode { get; }

{
    [Pulumi.OutputType]
    public sealed class CatalogTablePartitionKey
    {
        public readonly string? Comment;
        public readonly string Name;
        public readonly string? Type;
    }
    [Pulumi.OutputType]
    public sealed class CatalogTableStorageDescriptor
    {
        public readonly System.Collections.Immutable.ImmutableArray<string> BucketColumns;
        public readonly System.Collections.Immutable.ImmutableArray<Pulumi.Aws.Glue.Outputs.CatalogTableStorageDescriptorColumn> Columns;
        public readonly bool? Compressed;
        public readonly string? InputFormat;
        public readonly string? Location;
        public readonly int? NumberOfBuckets;
        public readonly string? OutputFormat;
        public readonly System.Collections.Immutable.ImmutableDictionary<string, string>? Parameters;
        public readonly Pulumi.Aws.Glue.Outputs.CatalogTableStorageDescriptorSerDeInfo? SerDeInfo;
        public readonly Pulumi.Aws.Glue.Outputs.CatalogTableStorageDescriptorSkewedInfo? SkewedInfo;
        public readonly System.Collections.Immutable.ImmutableArray<Pulumi.Aws.Glue.Outputs.CatalogTableStorageDescriptorSortColumn> SortColumns;
        public readonly bool? StoredAsSubDirectories;
    }
    [Pulumi.OutputType]
    public sealed class CatalogTableStorageDescriptorColumn
    {
        public readonly string? Comment;
        public readonly string Name;

    public class Activity : Pulumi.CustomResource
    {
        public Activity(string name, Pulumi.Aws.Sfn.ActivityArgs? args = null, Pulumi.CustomResourceOptions? options = null) { }
